{{otheruses|Treasure Trails reward|the player owned house painted armour|Painted heraldic armour}}
'''Heraldic armours''' are cosmetic [[armour]] rewards from Easy to Hard [[Treasure Trails]]. Heraldic armour come in [[black equipment|black]], [[adamant equipment|adamant]], and [[rune equipment|rune]] varieties. The armour set only includes a helmet and a shield, whose stats are equivalent to a [[full helm]] and [[kiteshield]] of the same metal. There are five different heraldic designs in total.

